  "title": "Service Crew / Salad Artist",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Hiring: Full Time/Part Time Salad Artist </strong>(5-Day or 6-Day shift)</p><p><strong>Working Days</strong>: Monday–Friday or Monday-Saturday, Public Holidays Off</p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Singapore Downtown / Central Region</p><p><strong>All are welcome to apply!</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Join our team and be a part of something fresh! If you're passionate about nutritious food and creating a positive, energetic environment, we'd love to have you on board!</p><ul><li>Greet and assist customers with their needs</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of service counters and dining area</li><li>Help with daily setup, closing, and inventory checks</li><li>Provide warm and helpful service, address customer needs</li><li>Collaborate with team members to support store operations</li><li>Prepare and execute salad bowls made to order, including simple meal prep</li><li>Perform cleaning tasks to maintain the store's environment</li><li>Understand and adhere to food safety policies and procedures</li></ul>",
